(28, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'About', 'Published', 'about', 'en', 'About', '<p>First and foremost, we&nbsp;are PASSIONATE about nurturing creativity!</p>\r\n<p>What does that mean for us? Well, we love having fun with different materials - paint,&nbsp;glue and, of course, a bit of glitter &ndash; but we also believe that being creative is about experimenting, playing and just seeing what happens.</p>\r\n<p>Giving expression to your own imagination in a group setting provides lots of benefits. It helps young children learn to make choices, share, listen,&nbsp;observe, pretend, problem solve, as well as play and&nbsp;interact with others.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Creation Station isn&rsquo;t simply about learning how to paint, model or collage along the lines of &ldquo;Here&rsquo;s one we did earlier&rdquo;. It&rsquo;s all about having a go, being inspired by something quite simple and&nbsp;encouraging each person to develop their own ideas. It&rsquo;s amazing seeing that happen and it also gives you a huge boost of confidence when your ideas are taken seriously - no matter how old you are!</p>\r\n<p>We hope you find these pages inspiring and that we can&nbsp;help kindle your child&rsquo;s own journey of discovery&nbsp;and love of learning.</p>\r\n<p><a href="admin/how-we-started">How we started &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<div class="cssRule cssEditableRule insertInto editGroup ">\r\n<p><a title="Our Values &amp; Passion" href="admin/Our-Values-Passion">Our Values, Passion and Day Dreams &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>The Creation Station Ltd is registered in England and Wales under registered number 05249876.<br />The VAT registration number is 982 9299 53</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Registered address</strong><br />The Creation Station Ltd | Inspiration House l Creativity Drive l Unit 3 | Woodbury Business Park&nbsp;| Woodbury l Devon | EX5 1LD</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 15px;"><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="admin/admin/admin/admin/upload/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="" width="293" height="43" /></a></p>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 8, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(29, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'How we started', 'Published', 'how-we-started', 'en', 'How we started', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m Sarah Cressall, founder of The Creation Station and mum to three lively boys. As a parent, I know how important it is to feel that you&rsquo;re bringing out the best in your children but I also know, from trial and error, just how difficult that can be!</p>\r\n<p>Creativity has always been a passion of mine. Even when I worked as a senior manager in London, I pursued my love of art and design &ndash; selling my artwork, as well as completing murals at Charing Cross for British Telecom and Exeter University!</p>\r\n<p>After gaining an Art Management Diploma, I became head of Art and Photography in a young adults&rsquo; disabled centre. I also ran my own design business &ldquo;Artworks&rdquo; and continued to win commissions for my creative work. These experiences sowed the seeds of what would later become The Creation Station.</p>\r\n<h3>Becoming a mum!</h3>\r\n<p>Having children brought a very different focus to my life, especially when it came to keeping them occupied. In their early years I tried really hard to provide creative &ldquo;messy time&rdquo; but the boys would usually only sit still for a couple of minutes, then announce they&rsquo;d finished while I was still setting up!</p>\r\n<p>It was hard to actually enjoy these activities with them as I was too busy getting everything out, washing&nbsp;up and trying to clean <em>them</em> up before they charged through the house.</p>\r\n<h3>Creating something different</h3>\r\n<p>I realised it must be the same for many other mums and dads and set about creating an experience that children and their parents or carers could enjoy together. This was back in 2002. I spent the next five years steadily developing the idea of arts and crafts activity sessions which took families on a shared journey of discovery.</p>\r\n<p>My aim was to inspire children''s natural creativity at an early age in a safe and nurturing environment using art, craft, music and movement. Not only was it great for children''s development but it was really good fun to do this creative stuff <em>with</em> your child, especially when &lsquo;mess'' wasn&rsquo;t an issue, and all the planning and clearing up was done by somebody else.</p>\r\n<p>The sessions &ndash; which have already been enjoyed by thousands of parents and children - are designed within the Every Years Foundation Stage (EYFS) of the Department of Education&rsquo;s framework. They take into account The Early Goals for pre-school children to help them practise and develop their skills in preparation for school.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 9, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(30, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Our Values Passion', 'Published', 'our-values-passion', 'en', 'Our Values Passion', '<p>Giggles of excitement as the magic box appears, children creating artworks they&rsquo;ll treasure, sticky fingers, painted arms and noses, chatting and laughing Mums, squelchy and squishy stuff, sparkly and glittery trails&hellip; these are the things we take pride in at the Creation Station!</p>\r\n<p>We firmly believe that our future is in the hands of our children and that we need to give them the tools, skills and passion to discover and embrace all the wonders of the world.</p>\r\n<p>We love feeling excited about Monday mornings, and every activity we organise, because what we do <em>matters</em> to us. And that&rsquo;s why our smiles are genuine!</p>\r\n<p>We&nbsp;feel privileged to be able to release the magic of childhood discovery and creative play and the many benefits they bring. It&rsquo;s about firing up our children&rsquo;s imagination and setting them off on a journey of discovery.</p>\r\n<p>Be inspired... what will you discover today?"</p>\r\n<p><a href="admin/contact"><img src="admin/upload/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="" width="293" height="43" /></a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 1, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(31, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Toddler Preschool Childrens Art Craft Classes', 'Published', 'toddler-preschool-childrens-art-craft-classes', 'en', 'toddler-preschool-childrens-art-craft-classes', '<p><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/tJ2Ca9KreZ0&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object></p>\r\n<h4>Children of all ages really benefit from being involved&nbsp;in art and craft activities. It''s not necessarily about the end product, but the exciting and absorbing journey they go on to create their own masterpiece.</h4>\r\n<p>These experiences help to build essential and desirable life skills, and the best bit - children LOVE arts and craft!</p>\r\n<p>In the right environment, where children are free to explore, discover and try out their own ideas, they engage in their own way and flourish.</p>\r\n<p>We know it can be tricky to provide these experiences at home&nbsp;- so that&rsquo;s why we&rsquo;re here!</p>\r\n<p>Our exciting and educationally-based workshops&nbsp;are tailored to your child. And for you, there&rsquo;s no stress or mess to worry about. The end result: essential quality time with your child in a safe and friendly environment.&nbsp;Above is the Sky TV feature about the experiences but the best way to find out more is to come along and experience the hands on fun with your own child. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We have a growing network of Creation Stations across the UK. Find out where your&nbsp;closest&nbsp;<a title="childrens classes" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">children''s classes</a>&nbsp;are.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Award Winning Exploration Classes</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Please click on the following links to find out more about how our classes work:</p>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art and Craft Classes" href="admin/admin/admin/admin/admin/crm.checksample.co.uk/Toddler-Art-Classes/">Toddler art and crafts classes &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Family-Holiday-Classes/" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Family-Holiday-Classes/">Holiday Time Classes - family fun&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How do the childrens art classes work" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/baby-toddler-preschool-arts-crafts-classes">How do the toddler classes work? &gt;&gt;<br /></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="The Science behind the Toddler Art Classes" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Science-Behind-The-Toddler-Art-Activities/">The science behind the fun &gt;&gt;<br /></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Safe--Responsible/">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 10, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(32, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Toddler art classes 1â€“5 years', 'Published', 'toddler-art-classes-15-years', 'en', 'Toddler art classes 1â€“5 years', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft"><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/RMiIRcYir7E&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" height="344" width="425" /></object>\r\n<h4>Baby, toddler and preschool&nbsp;art&nbsp;classes&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em;">The benefits of children sharing creative play with&nbsp;their parent or key carer are well documented. However, it can be tricky providing your baby, toddler or preschool child with hands-on arts and crafts activities at home.</span></p>\r\n<p>As busy parents we can all struggle with ideas, time or energy and the thought of the clearing up afterwards can feel anything but fun! Also it&rsquo;s often the case that by the time you&rsquo;ve set something up, they&rsquo;ve already finished!</p>\r\n<p>We totally understand this. In fact, that&rsquo;s precisely why the Creation Station was established - to give&nbsp;<strong>you</strong>&nbsp;quality, fun, creative experiences with your child in a safe, nurturing and friendly environment.</p>\r\n<p>Our award winning&nbsp;<strong>&lsquo;Exploration&rsquo; </strong>toddler art classes for babies,&nbsp;toddlers and preschool children provide the perfect solution for all your child''s creativity needs, with no stress or mess for you!</p>\r\n<p>Here''s how our weekly 50 minute&nbsp;<strong>&lsquo;Exploration''</strong>&rsquo; arts and crafts activity&nbsp;classes can inspire your child''s own journey of discovery and learning:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Explore ideas</li>\r\n<li>Discover what happens when...</li>\r\n<li>Develop important skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We are passionate about inspiring imaginations while helping you to have fun with your little one too.</p>\r\n<p><a title="The Creation Station" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/franchise-map/" target="_blank" rel="external"><em>Click here to find your nearest centre.</em></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 11, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(33, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Children''s art and craft classes', 'Published', 'childrens-art-and-craft-classes', 'en', 'Children''s art and craft classes', '<div id="contentBlockLeft"><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/tJ2Ca9KreZ0&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" height="344" width="425" /></object>\r\n<h4>Children of all ages really benefit from being involved&nbsp;in art and craft activities. It''s not necessarily about the end product, but the exciting and absorbing journey they go on to create their own masterpiece.</h4>\r\n<p>These experiences help to build essential and desirable life skills, and the best bit - children LOVE arts and craft!</p>\r\n<p>In the right environment, where children are free to explore, discover and try out their own ideas, they engage in their own way and flourish.</p>\r\n<p>We know it can be tricky to provide these experiences at home&nbsp;- so that&rsquo;s why we&rsquo;re here!</p>\r\n<p>Our exciting and educationally-based workshops&nbsp;are tailored to your child. And for you, there&rsquo;s no stress or mess to worry about. The end result: essential quality time with your child in a safe and friendly environment.&nbsp;Above is the Sky TV feature about the experiences but the best way to find out more is to come along and experience the hands on fun with your own child. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We have a growing network of Creation Stations across the UK. Find out where your&nbsp;closest&nbsp;<a title="childrens classes" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">children''s classes</a>&nbsp;are.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Award Winning Exploration Classes</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Please click on the following links to find out more about how our classes work:</p>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art and Craft Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years">Toddler art and crafts classes &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Family-Holiday-Classes/" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/family-holiday-classes-years">Holiday Time Classes - family fun&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How do the childrens art classes work" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-the-toddler-classes-work">How do the toddler classes work? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="The Science behind the Toddler Art Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/the-science-behind-the-toddler-art-activities">The science behind the fun &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/safe-responsible">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 12, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(34, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Family holiday classes 1â€“11 years', 'Published', 'family-holiday-classes-years', 'en', 'Family holiday classes 1â€“11 years', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>Looking for fun holiday activities for the kids that they&rsquo;ll love and won''t cost you a fortune?</p>\r\n<h4>Our holiday activities are the perfect solution.</h4>\r\n<p>Our kids&rsquo; art and crafts classes are suitable for 1 - 11 year olds so there&rsquo;s no problem with siblings of different ages.</p>\r\n<p>What so many of our parents love is that they can bring the whole family, even visiting relatives and friends, and the children will all enjoy it and want to come back.</p>\r\n<p>These classes don''t run all the time and do get full so please check you&nbsp;<a title="Local Childrens Art &amp; Craft Activities" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">local Creation Station</a>&nbsp; and please join our mailing list if you want to have first refusal on these popular&nbsp;and creative family workshops.</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 13, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(35, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Become A Franchisee', 'Published', 'become-a-franchisee', 'en', 'Become A Franchisee', '<p><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/0TSLYWAbsNE&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="500" height="400" /></object></p>\r\n<h4><strong>These pages are here to help you discover whether running your own Creation Station is the opportunity you have really been looking for.</strong></h4>\r\n<p>These are not&nbsp; &lsquo;sales'' pages, as we know the importance of finding the right people to join our team to deliver our values and share our passion about inspiring imaginations.</p>\r\n<p>Please take a look at each page on the site. We''ve tried to structure it so that you get an accurate picture of the opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>Our growing network of franchisees all came on board with different backgrounds - you can read how Lou wanted a flexible working, Ali needed a rewarding&nbsp;work life balance, and these stories are very inspiring.</p>\r\n<p><a title="Best opportunities" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Follow our Best Creative Opportunities Blog to keep up to date with new stories and offers</a></p>\r\n<p>You will see many comments from Mums, Dads and organisations&nbsp;on the website, about how they have benefitted from the Creation Station, so you know that this product works!</p>\r\n<p>Then there''s the about us section. We think this is important that you have all the details about us and what are values are. We are committed to ensuring we&nbsp;comply with the highest standards of&nbsp;best practise, to provide a professional, fair and ethical&nbsp;business for all our franchsiees.&nbsp;&nbsp;This&nbsp;demonstrates that we can be trusted to get it right, to work closely with you and to go the extra mile when it comes to guiding, supporting and assisting you, if you''re right for this business and you come on board with us. <br /><br />So enjoy having a browse and finding out about our business - and what it could be like as your business - and don''t forget to book in your "Discover Chat"</p>\r\n<p>In the meantime, if you''ve any questions give us a call&nbsp;or&nbsp;send us an email&nbsp;and we''ll be happy to answer them for you.</p>\r\n<p>Call Maggie on &nbsp;<span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395239700" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 239700</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>or email;&nbsp; <a href="http://mce_hostmailto:franchise@thecreationstation.co.uk/">franchise@thecreationstation.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p>You may find the following link to our blog helpful too;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>&gt;&gt;&nbsp;<a title="Best Opportunities" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">Discover what happens behind the scenes and true life stories of franchise owners</a></strong></h4>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 14, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(36, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'What our customers say', 'Published', 'what-our-customers-say', 'en', 'What our customers say', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p><em>To view our short film and hear what our customers think, please scroll to the bottom of this page</em></p>\r\n<p>We''re always looking for new ways to make the Creation Station service even better. We recently carried out a survey of 67 parents and carers who had come along to Creation Station &lsquo;Exploration'' toddler activity classes&nbsp;for more than five weeks. This is what they said:</p>\r\n<p><strong>100% said that attending the sessions had:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>increased their child''s concentration</li>\r\n<li>provided them with ideas of things to do at home</li>\r\n<li>given them fun, quality time with their child</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Without exception, they also said that they would refer a friend and many of them had!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Over 95% of parents/carers said that attending the Creation Station sessions:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>developed their child''s speech and language</li>\r\n<li>developed their child''s hand and eye co-ordination skills</li>\r\n<li>developed their child''s self confidence within a group</li>\r\n<li>was good value for money.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years">Toddler Art Classes&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What happnes in a children art class" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party">What happens in&nbsp;a class? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Science Behind The Fun" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/the-science-behind-the-toddler-art-activities">The science behind the fun &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/safe-responsible">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a> <object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/zskGU51nWus&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" height="344" width="425" /></object></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 15, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(63, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Arty Party', 'Published', 'arty-party', 'en', 'arty-party', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em;">Our Arty Party entertainer is the perfect hassle-free, affordable solution for special celebrations.</span></p>\r\n<p>Give your child a fun, creative experience to enjoy with their friends. More than just a simple event, our&nbsp;craft-making parties entertain and inspire too.</p>\r\n<p>Our parties are tailored around your child and great fun for you too, giving you less to do.</p>\r\n<p>All the children are inspired to create at least two original art pieces to take home and our art parties all include painting, modelling, making, sculpting, and crafting. Of course, music, dancing and games are provided too!</p>\r\n<p>You can relax because, as well as setting up and providing all the fun party activities, your Arty Party entertainer will also provide the invitations and party bags. Perfect!</p>\r\n<p>For further offers, ideas and competitions <a class="purple" title="The Creation Station Facebook page " href="http://www.facebook.com/thecreationstationltd" target="_blank" rel="external">like our Facebook page.</a> We hope you find this helpful.</p>\r\n<p><a style="line-height: 1.2em;" title="What happens at a craft party" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Childrens-Craft-Party-Entertainer/">What happens at a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/arts-crafts-party-packages-price">Party packages &amp; pricing &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How to book party entertainer" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/How-to-book-a-party-entertainer/">How to enquire and book a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<h3><strong><a title="Your Creation Station Arty Party Provider" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/franchise-map/" target="_blank" rel="external">Contact Your Local &nbsp;Creation Station Arty Party Fun Provider&nbsp;</a></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 42, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(37, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Childrens Activity Franchise', 'Published', 'childrens-activity-franchise', 'en', 'Childrens Activity Franchise', '<p><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/-aZNfhDrCzo&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object></p>\r\n<h3>Are you looking to be your own boss and earn good money whilst running your own successful children&rsquo;s creative experience business?</h3>\r\n<p><br />It''s no secret that looking for a career to bring in extra money and that makes a difference to others can be daunting.So why not follow in the footsteps of leading Business Woman of the Year and founder of The Creation Station Ltd, Sarah Cressall and discover the perfect answer to your dilemma.</p>\r\n<p><br />Sarah knows first hand how hard it can be to find a career that really gives you what want to achieve. As a mum to three, Sarah wanted a degree of flexibility between work and home life. At the same time Sarah knew she needed a sociable and rewarding career that could make a difference to others and contribute to the family pot. She couldn''t find anything available that met all these important needs. Sarah quickly identified a gap in the market for children''s creative art and crafts fun, and has developed an amazing business opportunity for a rewarding, succesful and flexible career.</p>\r\n<h3>Great news for Dynamic People!</h3>\r\n<p>So if you''re looking for a new direction and want to do something exciting and very rewarding as well as payiny you a good income at the same time, then you''ll want to find out more how Sarah is inspiring people across the nation.Here''s your chance to discover an opportunity that could give you the time and money you want in your life now.<br />And this is just the tip of the iceberg!<br />Here''s how you can start a career and really boost your income, by running your own successful award winning creative business.</p>\r\n<p><br />However we know this isn&rsquo;t right for everyone, so to find out more if this could be right for you give us a call for a chat.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><em><a title="best creative opportunities" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Follow our blog to keep up dated with true life stories and what happens behind the scenes at Creative Hub</a></em></h4>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 16, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(38, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'How the toddler classes work', 'Published', 'how-the-toddler-classes-work', 'en', 'How the toddler classes work', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<h3>How do the toddler classes work?.</h3>\r\n<p>The &lsquo;Exploration'' toddler&nbsp;classes run weekly during term times for 50 minutes. Our educationally based programme is underpinned by the Early Years Foundation Stage and runs during the term time for 12 - 14 weeks. Each programme is themed and has been developed exclusively for The Creation Station to cover&nbsp;key requirements to help children achieve their own journey of learning and early learning goals.</p>\r\n<h3>I have more than one child under five can I bring them both&nbsp;along?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes - absolutley. Our aim is to make your life easier and we tailor the activities to suit your children and their age and stage. We know that if you have more than one child, it''s hard trying to juggle activities that suit the different age ranges. That is why we run an all age inclusive class, making your life easier and supporting your family to have fun together!</p>\r\n<p>There are also many benefits of children being creative among children, especially in mixed age groups. The younger ones gain so much from mixing and observing the older children and the older ones can share their ''wisdom'', skills and top tips with the little ones.</p>\r\n<p>Plus we offer massive discounts on the cost for more than one child from the same family, and for childminders too making it even easier for you to enjoy some real creative family fun time together.</p>\r\n<h3>Can I come and try a session first?</h3>\r\n<p>You and your child are very welcome to come along to&nbsp;a couple of&nbsp;classes first, to decide whether you both love it! To book these two sessions, just find your <a title="Nearest childrens arts and crafts " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">nearest Creation Station</a> then book online, email or give them a call. It''s that easy.</p>\r\n<h3>What if I can''t come to all the classes in a programme?</h3>\r\n<p>If you let us know and there''s space, you''re very welcome to come to another class&nbsp;at a different time or day&nbsp;that week. Unfortunately we can''t carry over sessions that are missed from one week to another.</p>\r\n<p>We know how frustrating it is to pay for sessions and not be able to come to them all, so we''ve introduced a Voucher Scheme. These vouchers allow you to pre-book the sessions you can attend. So, if you can only make a few sessions, you don''t have to pay for the whole term.</p>\r\n<p>Session Vouchers also make great gifts. Maybe you know someone who''d like to treat your child to the sessions? Or perhaps you''re stuck for a special gift idea? Discover more about Creation station Classes Gift Vouchers.</p>\r\n<h3>Do I have to stay?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes. You or the parent/carer&nbsp;are responsible for&nbsp;your child during the session and&nbsp;we do encourage you to get involved during the activities and to have a go yourself! Evidence suggests that children gain far more confidence when their parent/carer is actively encouraging and supporting them in their explorations - plus it is quite good fun!</p>\r\n<h3>What does my child need to bring?</h3>\r\n<p>They don''t have to bring anything. However, if your child has been inspired during the week, they can bring in items to use during the session. Or if they have a particular project they want to get on with, they''re welcome to bring that in too.</p>\r\n<p>For your first two taster sessions we''ll supply the overalls for your child and we just recommend that you don''t wear your best! Just a note on the paints we use - they''re all non toxic, environmentally friendly and washable. If you do get the paint on an item of clothing it''s best to soak any paint stains in warm water or &lsquo;Vanish'' first, and then wash immediately.</p>\r\n<h3>My child just runs about and can''t sit still. Shall I wait until they''re a bit older as I don''t want to disrupt the class?</h3>\r\n<p>100% of customers surveyed said that their child''s concentration had increased due to attending the preschool classes.</p>\r\n<p>Please see our&nbsp;<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-our-customers-say">arts and crafts session survey </a>for more details. Many children who come need to run about for a bit. That''s what many children like to do as they explore their new environment, and that''s quite OK. Eventually, over the weeks, they''ll become more interested in what everyone else is doing. We recommend that&nbsp;you do the activities, then &nbsp;they come and see what you''re doing and will start to join in - it works like magic!</p>\r\n<h3>Can we bring friends or visiting cousins?</h3>\r\n<p>Yes. You''re very welcome to enjoy the session with&nbsp;friends and family. They can attend for a one off session. If you can, please call us just to let us know.</p>\r\n<h3>How do I book?</h3>\r\n<p>We request that you pre book so that we can welcome your child and prepare all the materials and tools that we will be using for that weeks arts and crafts class. Fees are paid termly, or with a post dated cheque for the second half term (depending on whichever method is more convenient for you). Due to demand, often by older siblings or friends who want to come too we also run half term and holiday activities for up to 11 years. Please join our mailing list to keep updated on our activities, classes and events in you local area.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 19px;">Can I buy your art and craft products to use at home?</span></p>\r\n<p>You can buy any of the art and craft products that are used during the sessions. We often have some of our &lsquo;Inspiration'' items for sale after the session if your child wants to carry on the activity, or if they want to develop an idea further at a later date.</p>\r\n<p>Alternatively, you can buy arts and crafts products from the &lsquo;Inspiration'' shop on this website.</p>\r\n<p>Here are some link that you may find useful;</p>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years">Toddler Art Classes&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What happnes in a children art class" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party">What happens in&nbsp;a class? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Science Behind The Fun" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/the-science-behind-the-toddler-art-activities">The science behind the fun &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/safe-responsible">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 17, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(64, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Group Events', 'Published', 'group-events', 'en', 'Group Events', '<h3>Discover how your group, event or organisation can benefit from the Creation Station&rsquo;s award-winning portfolio of arts and crafts activities.</h3>\r\n<p>The Creation Station has inspired more than 100,000 children and families since 2002 with fun, creative workshops that provide exciting, nurturing and safe experiences for children.</p>\r\n<p>Amongst many wonderful partners that we have worked with, we are proud to be been the official Kidszone provder for The Olympics in Hyde Park for 15 days. This is where the film on the right was filmed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re proud that our programme, as well as being great fun, is in line with the Early Years Foundation Stage. We want to make these sessions available to as many people as possible and it&rsquo;s easy for us to come to you and tailor our art and craft activities to your group, organisation or event.</p>\r\n<p>Although children and their parents can have a brilliant time discovering arts and crafts, we know it can be difficult for carers, groups and organisations to organise these activities themselves. Often the mess and stress can overshadow the real benefits&hellip;</p>\r\n<h3>Until now!</h3>\r\n<p>Our bespoke arts and craft group and corporate event entertainment&nbsp;provides a fun and stress-free experience for all involved to enjoy together.</p>\r\n<p>Here''s how it works:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>We come to your location -</strong> and provide our award-winning, educational, fun sessions for you.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Choice of duration - </strong>weekly,&nbsp;monthly or occasionally depending on your requirements.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Tailored to your term -</strong>&nbsp;we can provide term-time themed sessions such as Easter, Christmas or whatever suits!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Bespoke - </strong>we work with you to provide sessions to suit your group.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Proven and safe -</strong> we only use safety-tested, age and stage appropriate tools, materials and ideas.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Totally-managed solutions - </strong>you have no planning to do, no storage is needed and there&rsquo;s no clearing up to worry about.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Expand your range - </strong>we do everything to provide your group with a greater choice of educational, fun and inspiring activities.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><a style="line-height: 1.2em;" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/who-we-work-with" target="_blank" rel="external">Who we work with &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What we do" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-we-do">What do we do&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Weddings: Top 10 Tips for Keeping children amused" href="http://thecreationstation.co.uk/Documents/" target="_blank" rel="external">Weddings: Top Ten Tips for keeping children amused</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Rewqust information arts and crafts provider" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/request-information">Request more information&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 43, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(39, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'The science behind the toddler art activities', 'Published', 'the-science-behind-the-toddler-art-activities', 'en', 'The science behind the toddler art activities', '<p>We don&rsquo;t want to blind you with science but here are the basics if you&rsquo;re interested in knowing a bit more about our unique methodology&hellip;&nbsp; As you may have gathered, it&rsquo;s based upon nurturing each child''s own journey of discovery and development&nbsp;and draws on a wide range of influences. These include:</p>\r\n<p>The Theory of Multiple Intelligences developed by Dr Howard Gardner, Steiner Waldorf, Maria Montessori, Edward de Bono''s Creative Thinking and Emilio Reggio''s 100 Languages of Children.</p>\r\n<p>Our approach to toddler&nbsp;art activities captures the child''s interest and gently increases their focus and attention span. It is also in line with the Early Years Foundation Stage.</p>\r\n<p>Research indicates that children benefit significantly when engaging in toddler art activities&nbsp;if their key person is involved and supports them through their learning experiences.</p>\r\n<p>Our approach helps with children''s development in a number of important areas:</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Creative development</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Personal, social and emotional development</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Communication, language and literacy</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Mathematical development</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Knowledge and understanding of the world</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Physical development</p>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years">Toddler Art Classes&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How do the childrens art classes work" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-the-toddler-classes-work">How do the toddler classes work? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What happnes in a children art class" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party">What happens in&nbsp;a class? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/safe-responsible">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/contact-us/"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 18, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(40, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Safe & responsible', 'Published', 'safe-responsible', 'en', 'Safe & responsible', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact">http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact</a>You can rest assured that we are very serious about providing our arts and crafts activities in a safe and responsible manner.</p>\r\n<p>Tools and materials are age and stage appropriate and comply with European safety guidelines, where appropriate.</p>\r\n<p>Paint is washable, non toxic and eco-friendly. (And for those children who love exploring the taste of it, it&rsquo;s also wheat and gluten free!)</p>\r\n<p>Wherever possible we use recycled paper and source our materials sustainably. In line with our recycling song, we aim to be as green as possible&hellip; and often we end up a bit rainbow-coloured too!</p>\r\n<p>Our Creation Station Leaders are all fully-trained and CRB checked and run risk assessments on all our tried and tested session plans.</p>\r\n<p>We respect your privacy and will&nbsp;<em>never</em>&nbsp;pass on your details to a third party.</p>\r\n<p><a title="Toddler Art Classes" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years">Toddler Art Classes&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How do the childrens art classes work" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-the-toddler-classes-work">How do the toddler classes work? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What happnes in a children art class" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party">What happens in&nbsp;a class? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Safe and responsible" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/safe-responsible">Our commitment to responsible and safe arts and crafts &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/contact-us/"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 19, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(41, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Is it right for you?', 'Published', 'is-it-right-for-you', 'en', 'Is it right for you?', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>This is a very important question, so let us ask you a few quick questions...</p>\r\n<p>1: Would you like to run a successful creative business that is flexible to fit around your commitments?</p>\r\n<p>2: Would you like to help children learn through creative arts and crafts?</p>\r\n<p>3: Would you like to earn money the fun way?</p>\r\n<p>4. Are you proactive, can you think on your feet and do you like arts and crafts?</p>\r\n<p>5. Are you prepared to use all your skills and work hard to run and manage your own successful business?</p>\r\n<p>6: Would you like to be part of a growing network and at the same time be your own boss and benefit from ongoing support on hand when you need it?</p>\r\n<h4>Is your answer a resounding YES?</h4>\r\n<p>Then you must take a serious look at &lsquo;The Creation Station'' franchise opportunity because this offers you a flexible business opportunity that''s affordable without all the hassles and risks of starting a business on your own.</p>\r\n<p>Imagine this...</p>\r\n<p><em>...building a satisfying career for yourself where you make a difference in your community and earning the income from your efforts.</em></p>\r\n<p>And just so you know you can run sessions all year round including holidays if you want to because there are many additional opportunities to help grow your business at a pace that suits you. With the potential to earn from &pound;25 per hour who wouldn''t want to get this?</p>\r\n<p>For an investment from &pound;5.500 plus Vat and a &pound;1000 working capital, you will receive everything you require to confidently run your own successful Creation Station franchise and you will become part of the UK''s leading creative activity providers that is committed to actively inspiring children''s imaginations.</p>\r\n<h4>Life doesn''t have to be about just going to work.</h4>\r\n<p>It can be tough finding a career that you love, but if you do love nurturing children''s imaginations then you can feel like you are making a difference to others.</p>\r\n<p>So here''s the Good News.</p>\r\n<p>We provide everything you need with ongoing support and help you have a successful career, earn extra money and effortlessly balance your family life. It''s all possible with &lsquo;The Creation Station'' franchise opportunity.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Prices for this comprehensive business start at just &pound;5,500 plus vat.&nbsp;With our contacts&nbsp;with the banks we can help you access a bank loan for upto 70% of the value, subject to terms. So you really have all the help you need to achieve what you are looking for.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>So what are you waiting for? Call Now For A Chat on <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395233022" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 233022</span></span></span></span></strong></h4>\r\n<p><strong><em><a title="best creative opportunity" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">Read what franchise owners say about running their own franchise on our best Creative Opportunities blog</a><a title="Blog" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0TSLYWAbsNE&amp;autoplay=1" target="_blank" rel="external">&nbsp;</a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><a title="Become a Franchisee" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/become-a-franchisee">Become&nbsp;A Franchisee&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Childrens Activity Franchise" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/childrens-activity-franchise">Childrens Activity Franchise &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Is It Right For You?" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/is-it-right-for-you">Is It Right For YOU? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Who Esle I sSaying Yes To Mums Franchise" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/who-else-is-saying-yes">Who Else&nbsp;Is Saying YES? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Read What Our Franchisees Say" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/read-what-our-franchisees-say">Read What Our Franchisees Say &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/kIC1IbwQyBw&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object></div>\r\n<div id="contentBlockRight">&nbsp;</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 20, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0);
