(42, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Competition Rules', 'Published', 'competition-rules', 'en', 'Competition Rules', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\n<p>You can win cool stuff, products and experiences through the many competitions that we run. If you would like to ensure you don''t miss out on any of our competitions receive our email newsletter for updates and ideas.</p>\n<p>&gt;&gt; <a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/newsletter/" target="_blank" rel="external">Receive competition details, updates and offers.</a></p>\n<p>Here''s the rules of our competition:</p>\n<p><strong>Please make sure you read and understand the terms and conditions below before entering our competition.</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 1.2em;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>To qualify to enter the competition you must enter the competition and must &nbsp;not be an employee or an agent of the Creation Station.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>To enter the competition, applicants must complete the competition form&nbsp; including accepting these terms and conditions, in order to qualify for the prize.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Incomplete entries or those not received by the end of the event will be disqualified.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The prize cannot be substituted for a cash alternative.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>In the event of any dispute regarding the rules, conduct or the results of the competition, the decision of The Creation Station&nbsp; shall be final.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Creation Station reserves the right to disqualify any applicant if it has reasonable grounds to believe the applicant has breached any of these terms and conditions.</li>\n<li>Entries will be judged by The Creation Station&nbsp; on the day of the event. The judge&rsquo;s decision is final.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Winning applicants will be contacted by The Creation Station and no correspondence will be entered into.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The winner''s name may be published online &nbsp;&nbsp;and in publications&nbsp; after the closing date of the competition.</li>\n<li>The winner may be requested to make themselves available for promotion or publicity for The Creation Station.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Creation Station reserves the right to cancel or amend the terms of this competition at anytime without prior notice. Any changes will be posted on <a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact">www.thecrreationstation.co.uk</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Competitions ran via a app on &nbsp;Facebook or via any other third party does not in anyway associate the third party with, or endorse the &nbsp;competition.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The competition and the terms and conditions of this agreement will be governed by English law. <br /> <br /> By entering this competition, applicants agree to be bound by the above terms and conditions.&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 21, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(43, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Arty Party entertainer', 'Published', 'arty-party-entertainer', 'en', 'Arty Party entertainer', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em;">Our Arty Party entertainer is the perfect hassle-free, affordable solution for special celebrations.</span></p>\r\n<p>Give your child a fun, creative experience to enjoy with their friends. More than just a simple event, our&nbsp;craft-making parties entertain and inspire too.</p>\r\n<p>Our parties are tailored around your child and great fun for you too, giving you less to do.</p>\r\n<p>All the children are inspired to create at least two original art pieces to take home and our art parties all include painting, modelling, making, sculpting, and crafting. Of course, music, dancing and games are provided too!</p>\r\n<p>You can relax because, as well as setting up and providing all the fun party activities, your Arty Party entertainer will also provide the invitations and party bags. Perfect!</p>\r\n<p>For further offers, ideas and competitions <a class="purple" title="The Creation Station Facebook page " href="http://www.facebook.com/thecreationstationltd" target="_blank" rel="external">like our Facebook page.</a> We hope you find this helpful.</p>\r\n<p><a style="line-height: 1.2em;" title="What happens at a craft party" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party">What happens at a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/party-packages-pricing">Party packages &amp; pricing &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How to book party entertainer" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-to-book-a-party">How to enquire and book a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<h3><strong><a title="Your Creation Station Arty Party Provider" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/franchise-map/" target="_blank" rel="external">Contact Your Local &nbsp;Creation Station Arty Party Fun Provider&nbsp;</a></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 22, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(44, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'What happens at a party?', 'Published', 'what-happens-at-a-party', 'en', 'What happens at a party?', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft"><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/Q97kHEq1ZiA&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" height="344" width="425" /></object>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let the fun commence... Children&rsquo;s imaginations are inspired as soon as they arrive as they can personalise and decorate their own party bags. With music, dancing, games and a little bit of magic, the children soon discover their hidden talents, expand their creativity and indulge their imaginations!</p>\r\n<p>Our renowned <strong>&lsquo;Magical Ideas Box'' </strong>is sure to delight and engage your child and all their guests as they discover what&rsquo;s inside&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>It could be a wooden box, which the children transform with paints, gemstones and glitter, or a stretched canvas to create their own personal masterpiece!</p>\r\n<p>After this first activity, we return to the box and try out the magic again...</p>\r\n<p>Balls of clay may appear to be transformed into four-legged creatures, or beautiful bowls with fluffy feathers. We&rsquo;re sure you get the idea!</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Let your child create.</strong>&nbsp;We give your child free rein to create a masterpiece that uses their imagination and creativity. We provide all the floor and table covers, overalls and materials so you can relax and enjoy the party!</li>\r\n<li><strong>Magical and memorable.</strong>&nbsp;The children proudly return home with a unique and treasured party bag, full of mementoes of a really special celebration.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Personal and professional.</strong>&nbsp;We make the activities very personal to your child and the venue you choose. You can have the party at home or in a hall. What''s more, we can even help you plan and set it up.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Because of increased demand, we now offer a third activity - perfect for when the children have had their food and before they go home. This gives them the opportunity to make a beaded key ring, piece of jewellery or a laser bracelet. The children are always keen to see if there is anything else in the <strong>Magical Ideas Box</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>so this activity keeps them entertained once they&rsquo;ve eaten. Parents love it!</p>\r\n<p>You can choose to have one hour or an hour and a half of thrilling, exciting, and inspiring fun!</p>\r\n<h4>Reassurance &amp; trust</h4>\r\n<p>Our Party Leaders are fully-trained, CRB checked, first aiders and insured.</p>\r\n<p>We use products that are safe, suitable and non toxic. We strive to use products from sustainable or recycled sources. Our eco-friendly paints are washable and come out&nbsp;of most fabrics.</p>\r\n<p>We give you a courtesy call a couple of days before the big event and arrive 45 minute before the party starts to meet and greet the party person and prepare all the fun activities!</p>\r\n<h4>Children (and parents) love our parties.</h4>\r\n<p>Do you want to join the many families who have really enjoyed <strong>Creation Station celebration parties?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Then give us a ring for a no obligation chat on our Party Hotline, 0845 050 8743. We''ll be happy to answer any questions you have.</p>\r\n<h4>Limited availability</h4>\r\n<p>We''re sure you''ll appreciate that with a popular activity like this dates get booked up well in advance. If you have a date in mind, we''d be happy to provisionally book it in to prevent you missing out.</p>\r\n<p><a title="Childrens Arty party" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/arty-party-entertainer">Arty Party &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Arts Crafts Party Packages &amp; Price" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/party-packages-pricing"><span style="color: #d70000;">Party packages &amp; pricing &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How to book party entertainer" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-to-book-a-party"><span style="color: #d70000;">How to enquire and book a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 23, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(45, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Party packages & pricing', 'Published', 'party-packages-pricing', 'en', 'Party packages & pricing', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>We absolutely love parties and our children''s Arty Party packages are designed to encourage girls and boys from 1 - 11 years to feel inspired, have fun and create a party bag filled with their own wonderful artworks. We also aim to make the party as stress free as possible for you. (In fact, what we really love is that&nbsp;grown ups love the parties as much as the kids and us!)</p>\r\n<p>We have three types of&nbsp;Arty Party packages and they are all&nbsp;tailored around your child, your needs, the size of your group and your budget. You can also choose to have your Arty Party at home, or in a venue. We work with you to make your child''s birthday the best day of their year and provide treasured memories for all involved.</p>\r\n<p>All options include each child decorating their own party bag, making and taking home at least two original artworks, plus music, games and dancing and complimentary party invitations. Their party bags are included so you have less to organise.</p>\r\n<p>Here are a few examples of our most popular making activities:</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Cool&nbsp;arty parties</strong></h4>\r\n<p><em>Creative creatures, beautiful butterflies and beastie bugs&hellip;!</em></p>\r\n<p>Create your own little pet creature from clay.&nbsp; After the food, make some gorgeous jewellery or laser bracelets.</p>\r\n<p><em>Princes and Princesses&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Paint and collage your own mask. Will it be pink and fluffy or dark and scary? Create your own headdress with willow and beads and wire to make a tiara fit for a princess or a prince&rsquo;s royal crown. After the food&nbsp;you could make your own royal pet out of clay.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Brilliant arty parties</strong></h4>\r\n<p><em>Create sparkly treasure&nbsp;chests and magical wands&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Decorate your own beautiful chest - transform it into a princess&rsquo; jewellery box, or a pirate&rsquo;s treasure chest. Afterwards create clay bowls to hold all those special gems then, after the food, adorn a beaded starry wand or funky willow fish.</p>\r\n<p><em>Be a designer and create your own T-shirt design&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Design, colour and paint your own Creation Station T-shirt. Finish off after the food by making jewellery with beads, bells and buttons.</p>\r\n<p><em>Create a canvas masterpiece&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Let your imagination fly with our exciting paint tools, sparkly sequins and collage materials. Create your own unique modern artwork on a professional stretched canvas then make a jingly, jangly key ring. &nbsp;After the food, make your own funky badge.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Awesome arty parties</strong></h4>\r\n<p>This is our bespoke package where you can choose from any of the activities and we put an original party together for you. Here are just a few popular choices:</p>\r\n<p><em>Art for you to treasure&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Paint and collage a wooden treasure chest and paint a stunning art canvas. After the food, make some wonderful willow wands and headdresses.</p>\r\n<p><em>Creative kids&hellip;</em>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Design a T- shirt and willow headdress and bracelets.</p>\r\n<p><em>Fantastic art to display&hellip;</em></p>\r\n<p>Give your imagination free rein - use our exciting paint tools, sparkly sequins and collage material to create your own unique modern artwork on a professional stretched canvas, and then create your own designer T-Shirt&nbsp;masterpiece too.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Prices</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Our parties are tailored to suit your needs and to help your child have a wonderful special celebration, there is no minimum number of children required to enjoy a fabulous Arty Party.</p>\r\n<p>For details of availability, and packages to suit your budget please contact your local Creation Station provider.</p>\r\n<p>We know that it&rsquo;s tricky knowing how many children will arrive on the day, so we&rsquo;ve&nbsp;created different price brackets depending on the party package you choose and the approximate number of children invited. This way you can have the perfect party to suit your preferences.</p>\r\n<p>Up to 10 children</p>\r\n<p>Up to 15 children</p>\r\n<p>Up to 20 children</p>\r\n<p>Up to 25 children</p>\r\n<p>Up to 30 children</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Special offers</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Your local Creation Station often has great&nbsp;special offers. Find your nearest Creation Station<a title="Arty Party Entertainer" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">&nbsp;Arty Party Entertainer</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;contact them directly. We recommend that you enquire about availability as soon as you can so that we can help to make your child''s day their best ever!</p>\r\n<p><a title="Childrens Arty party" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/arty-party-entertainer"><span style="color: #d70000;">Arty Party &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="What happens at a craft party" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-happens-at-a-party"><span style="color: #d70000;">What happens at a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<p><a title="How to book party entertainer" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/how-to-book-a-party"><span style="color: #d70000;">How to enquire and book a&nbsp;party &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 24, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(46, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Should you start your own franchise', 'Published', 'should-you-start-your-own-franchise', 'en', 'Should you start your own franchise', '<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>Did you know that the number of people who are now self-employed has increased by 573,000 since the recession of 2008-09 - a significant rise of 15%.</p>\r\n<p>There are many reasons why people choose to to run their own business. Many want a more flexible pattern of working, to reap the benefits of their own hard work and for many it is realising that if others can do it, why can''t I realise my dream too.</p>\r\n<p>But it is definitely not for everyone. It''s important to really understand what you want to achieve, whether you are&nbsp;self-motivated and pro-active because there is no ''boss'' telling you what to do and you need to be realistic about how hard you are prepared to work.</p>\r\n<p>Many of our 85 franchise owners hadn''t heard of franchising before when they came across The Creation Station and they didn''t have any business exprience beforehand. Interestingly, they all come from a wide variety of backgrounds, but they all wanted greater flexibility to meet and enjoy family and work commitments. They also value running their own award winning, tried and tested franchise, because all the know-how you need, is provided.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So if you''ve been thinking about running your own &nbsp;business and would like to find out more about whether this could be right for you&nbsp;or not, pop your details in below and click submit then give us a call on <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395239700" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 239700</span></span></span></span> to book your "15 min Discover Chat" with Maggie.</p>\r\n<p>We actually only award our franchise to 2% of enquirers because it''s really important that it''s right for both of us. I hope that make sense. That is the reason why we need to book in a &nbsp;''Discover Chat'' with you - it''s just an informal and honest chat to find out more about you and whether this could be right for you or not.</p>\r\n<p>Please note that you do&nbsp;need to be able to drive and the investment level starts at &pound;5,500 plus Vat, we may be able to assist with helping you gain a bank loan for up to 70%.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So if you''re starting to feel excited at the idea of running your own successful childrens creative franchise, we cant wait to hear from you! The number you need to call is <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395239700" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 239700</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; and speak with Maggie from our awards team. We look forward to hearing from you. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sarah Cressall</p>\r\n<h4>The Muma of The Creation Station</h4>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 25, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(47, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'How to book a party', 'Published', 'how-to-book-a-party', 'en', 'How to book a party', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>To book an original,&nbsp;stress-free, fun party, please find your closest Creation Station Arty Party entertainer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you can''t see a Creation Station close to you, please click on the&nbsp;nearest, as we are happy to travel to your preferred location for the party. To cover the travel costs there&nbsp;will be a small&nbsp;additional charge.</p>\r\n<p>Then, please just drop us an email,&nbsp;complete the&nbsp;enquiry form or pick up the phone for a chat and we&rsquo;ll help you work out the best party option for you.</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;a date and time has been agreed, we can reserve a slot for you for up to 5 days. This gives you time to find and check the availability of the venue of your choice.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To secure your booking, we request a &pound;50.00 deposit&nbsp;and on receipt of that we will send your complimentary party invitations.</p>\r\n<p>Before the event, we will give you a courtesy call to give you peace of mind that everything&rsquo;s in hand. It also allows us to confirm numbers and check if you have any other queries before the big day.</p>\r\n<p>It''s as simple as that!</p>\r\n<p>So check where your nearest&nbsp;<a title="Art Party Entertainer" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">Art Party Entertainer</a>&nbsp;is, or email <a href="http://mce_hostmailto:party@thecreationstation.co.uk/">party@thecreationstation.co.uk</a>&nbsp;with details of where you live, and we will help to create a memorable and fun birthday experience for your child, their friends and you too&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>You can call our Party Hotline on 0844&nbsp;854 9100 if you need help finding your nearest Arty Party entertainer.</p>\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Once you have confirmed availability and chosen the fun activities for your party, simply click<a title="Book Your Arty Party " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Thank-You-For-Booking-Your-Arty-Party/" target="_blank" rel="external">&nbsp;Book Your Arty&nbsp;Party&nbsp;Entertainer</a>&nbsp;to download your booking form with terms&nbsp;and conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 26, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(48, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Childrens Party Entertainer', 'Published', 'childrens-party-entertainer', 'en', 'Childrens Party Entertainer', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<h4>The Ultimate Fun Arts &amp; crafts Birthday Party entertainer</h4>\r\n<p>We love parties and our Arty Party entertainers operate across the UK and are fully trained in the Art of providing inspiring creative arty parties.</p>\r\n<p>Here is why so many people are booking us for their children''s birthday party;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>You can chose from many exciting activities</li>\r\n<li>Arty parties and tailored to your child and your budget</li>\r\n<li>You receive free funky invitations</li>\r\n<li>The creative party bags are decorated by the children and filled with all their unique artwork to take home in memory of a special birthday</li>\r\n<li>We can come to your home or to a venue of your choice</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>...and don''t forget we do it all - leaving YOU with less to do! (Doesn''t that sound good?)</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 27, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(49, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Who else is saying yes', 'Published', 'who-else-is-saying-yes', 'en', 'Who else is saying yes', '<p><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/kIC1IbwQyBw&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object></p>\r\n<h4>.. and wants to become one of our successful&nbsp;managers?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p>You''ll be pleasantly surprised at who decides to join this unique and rewarding business opportunity including:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Teachers</li>\r\n<li>Teaching Assistants</li>\r\n<li>IT Managers</li>\r\n<li>Business Managers</li>\r\n<li>Community Workers</li>\r\n<li>Guide Leaders</li>\r\n<li>And many others...</li>\r\n<li>And best of all...</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>...you don''t even need to be a budding artist or the next Blue Peter presenter! We provide you with everything you need to run a successful business but leave room to let your individual, creative flair shine through.</p>\r\n<h4>15,000 Parents &amp; Children Are Proof Enough!</h4>\r\n<p>The number of parents and children experiencing fun arts and crafts at their local Creation Station is increasing daily. There is urgent demand for sessions in areas not yet covered by existing franchisees. Plus the &lsquo;arty-party'', the Creation Station''s amazing children''s birthday party being much sought after by children and parents everywhere.</p>\r\n<h4>And this is only the beginning...</h4>\r\n<p>...the Creation Station franchisees have reported a significant increase in demand from organisations requesting our fun and professional activities to be run at their:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Nursery</li>\r\n<li>Preschool</li>\r\n<li>Play Group</li>\r\n<li>Art Centre</li>\r\n<li>Toddler Group</li>\r\n<li>Museum</li>\r\n<li>Soft Play Centre</li>\r\n<li>Family Event</li>\r\n<li>Children Centre</li>\r\n<li>Sure Start</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4>All this and more!</h4>\r\n<p>We''re sure you''ll agree this really is a proven system delivering professional and comprehensive activities for 1-11 year olds.</p>\r\n<h4>Just simply call <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+448450508743" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">0845 050 8743</span></span></span></span> for a chat - there is no obligation and it could really pay off, like it has for so many others. The personal and financial rewards you could receive from this proven franchise business could be the best thing you''ve said yes to in a long time.</h4>\r\n<p><a title="Become a Franchisee" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/become-a-franchisee">Become a Franchisee&nbsp;&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Childrens Activity Franchise" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/childrens-activity-franchise">Childrens Activity Franchise &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Mums Franchise Opportunity" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/is-it-right-for-you">Is it right for YOU? &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Read What Our Franchisee''s Say" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/read-what-our-franchisees-say">Read What Our Franchisees Say &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 28, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(50, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Event entertainment', 'Published', 'event-entertainment', 'en', 'Event entertainment', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\n<h2>Event entertainment</h2>\n<h3>Discover how your group, event or organisation can benefit from the Creation Station&rsquo;s award-winning portfolio of arts and crafts activities.</h3>\n<p>The Creation Station has inspired more than 100,000 children and families since 2002 with fun, creative workshops that provide exciting, nurturing and safe experiences for children.</p>\n<p>Amongst many wonderful partners that we have worked with, we are proud to be been the official Kidszone provder for The Olympics in Hyde Park for 15 days. This is where the film on the right was filmed.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We&rsquo;re proud that our programme, as well as being great fun, is in line with the Early Years Foundation Stage. We want to make these sessions available to as many people as possible and it&rsquo;s easy for us to come to you and tailor our art and craft activities to your group, organisation or event.</p>\n<p>Although children and their parents can have a brilliant time discovering arts and crafts, we know it can be difficult for carers, groups and organisations to organise these activities themselves. Often the mess and stress can overshadow the real benefits&hellip;</p>\n<h3>Until now!</h3>\n<p>Our bespoke arts and craft group and corporate event entertainment&nbsp;provides a fun and stress-free experience for all involved to enjoy together.</p>\n<p>Here''s how it works:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>We come to your location -</strong> and provide our award-winning, educational, fun sessions for you.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Choice of duration - </strong>weekly,&nbsp;monthly or occasionally depending on your requirements.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Tailored to your term -</strong>&nbsp;we can provide term-time themed sessions such as Easter, Christmas or whatever suits!</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Bespoke - </strong>we work with you to provide sessions to suit your group.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Proven and safe -</strong> we only use safety-tested, age and stage appropriate tools, materials and ideas.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Totally-managed solutions - </strong>you have no planning to do, no storage is needed and there&rsquo;s no clearing up to worry about.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Expand your range - </strong>we do everything to provide your group with a greater choice of educational, fun and inspiring activities.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a style="line-height: 1.2em;" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/arts-crafts-groups-events-provider" target="_blank" rel="external">Who we work with &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p><a title="What we do" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Arts-and-crafts-events-provider/">What do we do&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p><a title="Weddings: Top 10 Tips for Keeping children amused" href="http://thecreationstation.co.uk/Documents/" target="_blank" rel="external">Weddings: Top Ten Tips for keeping children amused</a></p>\n<p><a title="Rewqust information arts and crafts provider" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Book-a-arts-and-crafts-provider/">Request more information&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 29, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(51, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Read What Our Franchisees Say', 'Published', 'read-what-our-franchisees-say', 'en', 'Read What Our Franchisees Say', '<p><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/w-nCBFUYWG0&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object></p>\r\n<p>We are proud of our growing network of franchisees who support help to inspire imaginations across the nation. They all have a range of backgrounds and all got involved for different reasons.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hayley Sugden Creation Station Franchisee &ndash;&nbsp;Leeds</strong></p>\r\n<h4>"I&rsquo;ve found a fun and rewarding business that I love and that fits in perfectly with being mum to my boys &ndash; some people call me lucky &ndash; I tend to agree!"</h4>\r\n<p>"I wished there had been a Creation Station around when my twins were growing as it&rsquo;s so fabulous on many development levels giving inspiration and structure but also allowing you to explore with materials I couldn&rsquo;t use or didn&rsquo;t have room for at home.It has been over three years since I decided to invest in a Creation Station franchise with a view to finding a rewarding work/life balance after the birth of my twin boys. They join in at Creation Station wherever possible and love to get involved." &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a title="Mums franchise" href="http://yourcreationstation.wordpress.com/2013/02/13/ive-found-a-fun-and-rewarding-business-that-i-love-and-that-fits-in-perfectly-with-being-mum-to-my-boys-some-people-call-me-lucky-i-tend-to-agree/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Read Hayley&rsquo;s story&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Liz Cairns &nbsp;inspires imaginations with Creation Station in South Aryshire</strong></p>\r\n<h3>"I wanted to do something more rewarding with my time."</h3>\r\n<p>"I had enjoyed a really rewarding career in the hospitality industry, managing pubs and restaurants but when I had my son Jamie I decided a more flexible future would work better for me and my family, so I took a part time job as a receptionist. Although this was flexible, my brain and skills just weren&rsquo;t being used and I really wanted to be doing more than this with my life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a title="Rewarding flexible franchise" href="http://yourcreationstation.wordpress.com/2013/02/12/liz-cairns-talks-about-her-first-year-running-her-own-creation-station-franchise-in-south-ayrshire-scotland/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Read Liz&rsquo;s story&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Roisin Egan inspires imaginations in Mid Ulster, Northern Ireland&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<h3>"I swapped the suit, desk and briefcase for glitter, glue and clay!"</h3>\r\n<p>"I am so proud to have inspired over 1500 little imaginations in Mid-Ulster through sheer hard work in 5 months! I am proud to have 3 Weekly Little Explorer&rsquo;s classes ranging with between 7 &ndash; 16 children and a waiting list for one particular class . I have over 650 likes on my FB page. I&rsquo;m especially proud of the 16 event tenders that I&rsquo;ve won. &nbsp;I have been honoured to entertain at 12 children&rsquo;s Birthday Parties. I am proud to be part of such a supportive, energetic, understanding team &ndash; my Creation Station Family. You all rock!!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a title="mums franchise " href="http://yourcreationstation.wordpress.com/2013/02/14/i-swapped-the-suit-desk-and-briefcase-for-glitter-glue-" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Read Roisin''s story</a></p>\r\n<h4><strong>Jackie Farrow. Creation station Franchisee -&nbsp;Guildford</strong></h4>\r\n<p>What the Creation Station offered seemed almost too good to be true! A chance to turn an activity that I loved into my own business that I could fit around my two children, and expand as they grow older - it seemed to be the perfect <a title="Work-life balance franchise" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Work-Life-Balance-Franchise/">work-life balance franchise</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a title="franchise" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt;&nbsp;Read more true life stories on our blog</a></strong></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 30, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(52, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Discovery Mornings', 'Published', 'discovery-mornings', 'en', 'Discovery Mornings', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\n<h3>UK Discovery Mornings</h3>\n<a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/pageImages/be-inspired-be-inspiring-with-the-creation-station-logo-generic-copy.jpg" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/includes/thumb/phpThumb.php?src=/images/pageImages/be-inspired-be-inspiring-with-the-creation-station-logo-generic-copy.jpg&amp;w=203&amp;h=152&amp;zc=1&amp;f=png&amp;fltr[]=mask|/images/structure/img_right_mask.png&amp;fltr[]=wmi|/images/structure/overlay_copy.png|BR" alt="Discovery Mornings franchise image" width="203" height="152" /></a> <a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/pageImages/be-inspired-be-inspiring-with-the-creation-station-logo-generic-copy-1.jpg" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/includes/thumb/phpThumb.php?src=/images/pageImages/be-inspired-be-inspiring-with-the-creation-station-logo-generic-copy-1.jpg&amp;w=203&amp;h=152&amp;zc=1&amp;f=png&amp;fltr[]=mask|/images/structure/img_right_mask.png&amp;fltr[]=wmi|/images/structure/overlay_copy.png|BR" alt="Discovery Mornings franchise image" width="203" height="152" /></a>\n<p>One of the best ways to find out more is to attend one of our fun and informative Discovery Mornings.</p>\n<p>It''s a relaxed and informative morning that we can spend time together going through all your questions and how we support you to start, run and grow your very own Creation Station business in your area.</p>\n<p>Please scroll through&nbsp;our&nbsp;calendar to see the available dates and events we are running.</p>\n<p>Here you will learn all you need to know about how this family friendly income boosting opportunity puts you in control and provides you with the perfect work life balance.</p>\n<p>This is not a high-pressure sales pitch or one sided promotion event; it''s about discovering whether this is right for both of us.</p>\n<p>This event gives you everything you need to know about this exciting opportunity.</p>\n<p>Our next events are:</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-high-wycombe-march-15%20-%2028-03-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 18th April Guildford&nbsp;9:30 - 1:30</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-bristol-may-15%20-%2016-05-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 16th May Bristol - 9.30 - 1:30</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-bucks-june-15%20-%2013-06-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 6th June High Wycombe - 9:30 - 1:30</a></p>\n<p><a title="Franchise Discovery " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-manchester-july-15%20-%2018-07-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 18th July Manchester - 9:30 - 1:30</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-exeter-aug-15%20-%2015-08-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 15th August Exeter - 9:30 - 1.30</a></p>\n<p><a title="Franchise Discovery " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-surrey-sept-15%20-%2012-09-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 12th September Guildford - 9.30 - 1.30</a></p>\n<p><a title="Franchise Discovery " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-coventry-nov-15%20-%2017-10-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 17th October - Coventry -&nbsp;Ryton-on-Dunsmore</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-hemel-hempstead-nov-15%20-%2007-11-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 7th November Hemel Hempstead - TBC</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/childrens-art-class-and-party-entertainer/discovery-mornings/event/discovery-event-exeter-nov-15%20-%2028-11-2015" target="_blank">Saturday 28th November Exeter - 9:30 - 1:30pm</a></p>\n<p>Please choose&nbsp;a suitable date on&nbsp;the&nbsp;calendar. Then&nbsp;click on the coloured square. You will then be able to&nbsp;complete the pop up booking form&nbsp;and&nbsp;details about your Discovery Morning will be sent to you. <br />Before you attend a Discovery Event you will need to have your "Discover Chat" with Maggie so that we can be sure that this could be the right fit for you.</p>\n<p>Call us today on T: <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+447584102296" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">07584 102296</span></span></span></span> or <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395239700" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 239700</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>Or simply email <a href="mailto:maggie@thecreationstation.co.uk" target="_blank">maggie@thecreationstation.co.uk</a> to book your free place.</p>\n<p>To reserve your place we ask for a refundable &pound;20 payment. This will be refunded after you have attended the Discovery Morning. &nbsp;Just click on the Buy Now button below and in the comments let us know which Discovery Morning you would like to reserve.</p>\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input alt="PayPal &ndash; The safer, easier way to pay   online." name="submit" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/GB/i/btn/btn_buynowCC_LG.gif" type="image" /> <img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_GB/i/scr/pixel.gif" alt="" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></form>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We look forward to hearing from you.</p>\n<p>Kind regards<br />Sarah Cressall<br />&nbsp;</p>\n<object data="http://www.youtube.com/v/IhiJpDHaa_4&amp;list=UUkB4Z0S_Y8PYYh4zYMua3BQ&amp;index=3&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="300" height="150"></object>\n<p><a title="Back to Listing" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/franchise-map/">&laquo; Back to listing</a></p>\n</div>\n<div id="contentBlockRight">&nbsp;</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 31, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(53, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Who we work with', 'Published', 'who-we-work-with', 'en', 'Who we work with', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<h2>Who we work with</h2>\r\n<p>We work with a wide range of organisations to help them achieve community-focussed goals.</p>\r\n<p>We are proud to provide our&nbsp;specialist arts and crafts activities in line with the Early Years Foundation Stage and to work with the following groups and organisations:</p>\r\n<p>1. Preschool<br /><br />2. Playgroups<br /><br />3. Nurseries<br /><br />4. NCT groups<br /><br />5. Parenting classes</p>\r\n<p>6. Children&rsquo;s centre</p>\r\n<p>7. Sure Start<br /><br />8. Childminders<br /><br />9.Local council</p>\r\n<p>10.<a title="National Franchise Exhibition book The Creation Station" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/news/2010/09/the-national-franchise-exhibition-books-the-creation-station/" target="_blank" rel="external">National Franchise Exhibition</a></p>\r\n<p>11.<a title="National Event Entertainment" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/news/2010/6/family-event-entertainment/" target="_blank" rel="external">National Events and Shows</a></p>\r\n<p>12.<a title="events for children in national shopping centres" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/news/2010/06/shoppers-inspired-at-workshops/" target="_blank" rel="external">Shopping Centres</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>13.<a title="Inspiring dads at Barnardo''s group" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/news/2010/05/inspiring-dads-r-us-with-creation-station/" target="_blank" rel="external">Children''s charities</a></p>\r\n<p>14.Event Organisers</p>\r\n<p>15.Disability groups</p>\r\n<p>16.<a title="Dads group event entertainment" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/news/2010/05/inspiring-dads-r-us-with-creation-station/" target="_blank" rel="external">Dads&rsquo; groups</a></p>\r\n<p>17.Corporate events</p>\r\n<p>18.And many others</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>What do&nbsp;organisations say about working with us?</h4>\r\n<p>Those working in partnership with the Creation Station say it''s helped them achieve at least two of the following:</p>\r\n<p>Increase the number of 1- 5 year old visitors with their parents/carers.</p>\r\n<p>Attract new customers with a new award-winning experience.</p>\r\n<p>Create new groups to use the caf&eacute; or dining facilities.</p>\r\n<p>Retain customers for longer.</p>\r\n<p>Encourage new users and increase attendance.</p>\r\n<p>Provide staff with opportunities to observe and record children''s development.</p>\r\n<p>Provide staff with ideas and activities.</p>\r\n<p>Read more about our&nbsp;<a title="art and craft classes" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Toddler-Art-Classes/" target="_blank" rel="external">activities for preschool children</a>&nbsp;and playgroups</p>\r\n<p><a title="inspirational art and craft classes for preschoolers" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/toddler-art-classes-15-years" target="_blank" rel="external">Group Events&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-we-do">What do we do&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p><a title="Rewqust information arts and crafts provider" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/request-information">Request more information&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 32, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(54, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'What is it really like to run a Franchise?', 'Published', 'what-is-it-really-like-to-run-a-franchise', 'en', 'What is it really like to run a Franchise?', '<p>People&nbsp;have asked us "What''s it really&nbsp;like to run your own&nbsp;Creation Station Franchise?" So, we asked&nbsp;a couple of our franchisee''s to let you know.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>A big thank you to all those who let us share how much fun they were having and&nbsp;to Lisa, Aby &amp; Holly :) &nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p>Sit back and enjoy then dont forget to call us and book in your "Discover Chat" and if after your Discover Chat you feel this could be the right fit for you then Maggie would be delighted to invite you along to meet some of our franchisees for real at <a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/discovery-mornings">one of our Discovery Events.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="500" height="250">\r\n<source src="http://youtube.com/v/aZ2uokLQ0mM&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" /></video></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 33, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(55, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'What we do', 'Published', 'what-we-do', 'en', 'What we do', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\n<h2>What we do</h2>\n<h3>We can provide our exciting portfolio of award- winning arts and crafts activities and tailor the services to suit your needs.</h3>\n<h4>For baby or preschool settings...&nbsp;</h4>\n<p><strong>Exploration:</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Hands-on discovery for 3 month - 5 year olds with their parent/carer.</p>\n<p>The weekly sessions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>50 minutes during term time and holidays.</li>\n<li>Nurture and value each child''s own ideas.</li>\n<li>Support and engage the parent/carer in a sensitive and respectful manner.</li>\n<li>Provide consistently high-quality age and stage appropriate educational activities.</li>\n<li>Include seasonal and themed concepts and content.</li>\n<li>Provide simple ideas and free resources to use at home.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For holiday provision, events and shows...</h4>\n<p><strong>Imagination:</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Themed family arts and crafts, fun sessions for 1-11 year olds throughout the year. Great for holidays, fetes and events.</p>\n<h4>For having a good time...</h4>\n<p><strong>Celebration:</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Engaging activities for events, open days and special occasions - arts and crafts entertainment for 1-11 year olds. Arty Parties are an inspiring way to celebrate special events and occasions, like birthdays, open days, and leaving events.</p>\n<p><a title="Group Events" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/group-events">Group Events&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p><a title="Event &amp; Activity Partners" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/who-we-work-with">Who We work with &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p><a title="What we do" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/what-we-do">What do we do&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p><a title="Rewqust information arts and crafts provider" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/request-information">Request more information&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 34, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0);
